finalproject 0.1.0
  • Reference

    read csv file from USDA site and clean up.

    dataclean.Rd

    read csv file from USDA site and clean up.

    dataclean(url)

    Arguments

    url

    the csv file path.

    Value

    cleaned data.

    Author

    Zirou Zhou

    Examples

    dataclean("https://www.ers.usda.gov/webdocs/DataFiles/48747/Unemployment.csv")
